reviewText: If you love good music and appreciate a good voice, you must have this DVD in your collection, no wonder he earned the title "La Voz De America", you can appreciate him performe in his early years until recently, his voice is strong and beautiful as always. I wished they would have films when he used to sing with the trio "Los Tres Ases" along with Juanito Neri and Herctor Gonzalez,
